{"title":"Kubernetesの学习笔记","uid":"84c50d5ee6f451bc51fe31f3e7ac9569","slug":"20210621-01","date":"2021-06-20T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-06-24T07:25:57.803Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/20210621-01.json","keywords":null,"cover":"file/cover1.jpeg","content":"<p><em>Kubernetes</em><br>&emsp;&emsp; 容器编排的工具</p>\n<p><em>资源清单</em><br>&emsp;&emsp; Yam</p>\n<p>:::details 什么是资源？</p>\n<p>dd</p>\n<p>:::<br><em>Master</em> : 集群控制节点，每个集群需要至少一个master节点负责集群的管控<br><em>Node</em> : 工作负载节点，由master分配容器到这些node工作节点上，node上的docker负责容器运行<br><em>Pod</em> : Kubernetes的最小控制单元，容器都运行在pod中 一个pod中可以有一个或多个容器<br><em>Controller</em> : 控制器，通过它来实现对pod的管理 比如启动pod、停止pod、伸缩pod的数量的等。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8001/api/v1/namespaces/kubernetes-dashboard/services/https:kubernetes-dashboard:/proxy/\">http://127.0.0.1:8001/api/v1/namespaces/kubernetes-dashboard/services/https:kubernetes-dashboard:/proxy/</a></p>\n<p>获取key</p>\n<pre class=\"language-dart\" data-language=\"dart\"><code class=\"language-dart\">TOKEN<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>$<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>kubectl <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>n kube<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>system describe secret <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span> awk <span class=\"token string\">'$1==\"token:\"&#123;print $2&#125;'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nkubectl config <span class=\"token keyword\">set</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>credentials docker<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>desktop <span class=\"token operator\">--</span>token<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"$&#123;TOKEN&#125;\"</span>\necho $TOKEN</code></pre>\n\n<p>ifconfig | grep “inet”</p>\n<p><strong>服务分类</strong></p>\n<p>&emsp;&emsp; 有状态服务：数据库DBMS</p>\n<p>&emsp;&emsp; 无状态服务：LVS APACHE</p>\n<p><strong>Label</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span cla